    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Just wanted to chime in -- hit a brick wall with a similar issue for awhile before discovering this thread. I had `menu` widgets, which when prefiltered were not showing as selected. \r\n\r\nMy fix was also to change `facetsRefinements` to `hierarchicalFacetsRefinements`. Even though my facets are not hierarchical. Maybe update [the documentation](https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/documentation/#default-filters) to recommend using `hierarchicalFacetsRefinements` instead?\r\n\r\nThanks!",
